==English==
===Noun phrase===
'''[[proper]] [[subset]]''' (''plural'' '''proper subsets''')

#{{settheory}} Of a [[set]], a set that is a subset of the set but not equal to it.
#:''{2, 4, 5} is a proper subset of {1, 2, 3, 4, 5}, but {1, 2, 3, 4, 5} is not.''

